      "id": 1,
      "options": {
        "content": "## Request Trace\n\n把 `request_id` 填进顶部变量，然后从下往上看：先看 `HTTP`，再看 `Agent`，最后看 `Tool / Vision / Menu & Records`。\n\n推荐顺序：\n1. 确认是否真的进了后端\n2. 看状态码和耗时\n3. 看 Agent 走到哪个 phase\n4. 看 tool / vision / menu / records 哪一步异常\n\n如果请求在灰度槽位，就把 `backend_service` 切到 `backend_green`。",
        "mode": "markdown"
      },
      "title": "How To Use",
      "type": "text"
    },
